==Tailoring==
Kale is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a dyeable {{name|Shirt159|link=Tailoring{{!}}Shirt And Belt|class=inline}}. It is a green dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the green dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*Kale may be randomly requested in [[Spring]] (year 2+) at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|330}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

